msgid "You can assign tags created on a contact form under :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Customers` to identify what kind of customers have submitted the form. To do so, select a field in the form while in :guilabel:`Edit` mode, click the :guilabel:`+ Field` button under the :guilabel:`Style` tab, and set the field's :guilabel:`Type` to :guilabel:`Tags`. Toggle the tags that should be automatically assigned when a customer fills in the form and set the field's :guilabel:`Visibility` to :guilabel:`Hidden`."
