msgid "To create a new expertise, navigate to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Configuration --> Expertise` and click :guilabel:`New`. Enter the :guilabel:`Name` of the expertise, and, if desired, select one or more :guilabel:`Operators`. Click :guilabel:`Save` when finished."
