msgid "You can also duplicate one or several pages by going to :menuselection:`Website --> Site --> Pages`. Select the relevant page(s), click :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Actions`, and select :icon:`fa-files-o` :guilabel:`Duplicate`."
