msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:179
msgid "Access the page, then go to :menuselection:`Website --> Site --> Properties` and click :guilabel:`Delete Page`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:181
msgid "The :guilabel:`Delete Page` pop-up shows all links referring to the page you want to delete, organized by category. To ensure website visitors do not land on an error page, update all links on the website that refer to the page. To do so, expand a category, then click on a link to open it in a new window. Alternatively, you can set up a :ref:`redirection <website/pages/URL-redirection>` for the deleted page."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:186
msgid "Once you have updated the links (or set up a :ref:`redirect <website/pages/URL-redirection>`), tick the :guilabel:`I am sure about this.` checkbox, then click :guilabel:`Delete`."
