#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/website_creation.rst:61
msgid "The website import tool is a website scraper that searches for the specified website and analyzes it. It then uses custom AI models to rebuild it as an Odoo website. The extraction is performed page by page, preserving the original website's structure and content. Images, the sitemap, the :ref:`header <website/header_footer/header-design>`, and the :ref:`footer <website/header_footer/footer-design>` are also imported. Optionally, :doc:`product data <../ecommerce/configuration/products>` can also be extracted. The tool converts pages into standard Odoo :doc:`building blocks <web_design/building_blocks>`, making the imported website fully editable in Odoo."
